Flash Briefing Skill

des: Daily Conspiracy Briefing provides the user with an interesting fact about conspiracies each day as part of their Flash Briefing. Conspiracy Theories in this skill will cover events from the Area 51, JFK, 9/11, MLK, and many others. This Skill is designed to get people thinking about the major events that have happened in the past.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
